    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131680/extras/e81319ac0b6612db03fa43b12adf07d5.poster.avif?t=1744061040\" width=800 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131680/extras/e81319ac0b6612db03fa43b12adf07d5.webm?t=1744061040\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131680/extras/e81319ac0b6612db03fa43b12adf07d5.mp4?t=1744061040\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Blitz</strong> through <i>Stardust Valley</i>, experiencing everything from the spooky forest of <i>Blackthorn Mire</i> to the sunny sands of <i>Beachwood</i> -- and more! Perform <strong>sick tricks</strong> and skillful maneuvers to earn currency to unlock new boards. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131680/extras/0529d99cf1c3d71c0fada684558d46b0.avif?t=1744061040\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3131680/extras_big/0529d99cf1c3d71c0fada684558d46b0.avif?t=1744061040 width=800 height=254 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unique Skating Styles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick from 4 different skaters of <i>VchiBan</i> with their own unique powers and abilities to find the shredding style that grooves with you~!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >90s inspired visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Arcade style endless runner </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtrack </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ unique boards to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam leaderboards</p></li></ul>",
